{"tid":1258068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[割地] 中環海濱長廊將成解放軍用地","createTime":"2019-06-26T02:08:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T02:09:53.000Z","uid":5866,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"456881d988e042cc3bc1029afbb2abc9922ee181","tid":1258068,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:08:23.000Z","msg":"【緊急呼籲】中環海濱即將送中<br />\n立法會大會將於本周三(6月26日)審議由保安局提交的法案，五條附屬法例通過後，中環海濱長廊一幅150米長、面積約0.3公頃原為公眾「休憩用地」的範圍，將正式撥歸中國人民解放軍駐香港部隊作軍用碼頭之用！<br />\n<br />\n做法等同將中環海濱「送中」！香港人的海濱公共空間慘變成軍事用地，嚴重損害公眾利益！<br />\n<br />\n民主派立法會議員區諾軒將在會上動議廢除「海濱送中」議案；朱凱廸議員將動議將生效日期押後<br />\n<br />\n重點：條例係「先訂立後審議」，會係6月29日號自動生效！即係話，29號前如果無法通過區諾軒或朱凱廸議員嘅議案，條例將自動生效！係自動生效！！！！<br />\n<br />\n我們促請全體立法會議員支持廢除議案，不要強行通過惡法、製造社會矛盾！<br />\n<br />\n(當日議程：<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/counmtg/agenda/cm20190626.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr18-19%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Fagenda%2Fcm20190626.htm&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmUxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=38075c12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr18-19/chinese/counmtg/agenda/cm20190626.htm</a>)<br />\n<br />\n請加入促請全體立法會議員支持「廢除海濱送中」議案聯署：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2NdOvqJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NdOvqJ&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmUxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=d4792ffe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2NdOvqJ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Protect.Harbourfront/posts/931886437154697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FProtect.Harbourfront%2Fposts%2F931886437154697&d=BBPgAQHQe62%2Fb%2Fw120tVmUxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=8a634597\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Protect.Harbourfront/posts/931886437154697</a>"},{"pid":"635132257f8bdffa6fa3b8862de3c8a68a81c41d","tid":1258068,"uid":5866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T02:08:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass